          <!-- 常见问题 -->
          <section class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">常见问题</h2>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <details class="group" open>
                <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span>Q: 在中国不用代理能使用OpenAI的API吗？</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
                </summary>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2 text-sm">不能。OpenAI的API在中国大陆被封锁。你需要一个可用的代理或VPN服务，这增加了运维复杂度和潜在的可靠性问题。</p>
              </details>

              <div class="border-t pt-4">
                <details class="group">
                  <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span>Q: DeepSeek的模型质量够用于生产环境吗？</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
                  </summary>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2 text-sm">够用。DeepSeek-V3在大多数标准任务上与GPT-4o具有竞争力的表现。DeepSeek-R1在推理和代码任务上表现出色。对于大多数应用，DeepSeek模型完全足够。</p>
                </details>
              </div>

              <div class="border-t pt-4">
                <details class="group">
                  <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span>Q: 哪家提供商的免费额度最划算？</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
                  </summary>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2 text-sm">Google AI（Gemini 2.0 Flash无限免费）最大方，其次是DeepSeek（注册送$2）和OpenAI（新用户$5）。但免费额度均有速率限制。</p>
                </details>
              </div>

              <div class="border-t pt-4">
                <details class="group">
                  <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span>Q: Google AI在国内可以访问吗？</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
                  </summary>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2 text-sm">部分可以。部分Google AI服务在国内可以间歇性使用，但可靠性很差。对于生产应用，不要依赖直连访问。</p>
                </details>
              </div>

              <div class="border-t pt-4">
                <details class="group">
                  <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span>Q: 哪家最适合中文NLP任务？</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
                  </summary>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2 text-sm">DeepSeek由于中文训练数据丰富，通常在中文语言任务上表现良好。OpenAI的GPT-4o中文处理能力也不错。专业中文NLP可以考虑智谱或阿里云。</p>
                </details>
              </div>

              <div class="border-t pt-4">
                <details class="group">
                  <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span>Q: 切换提供商的难度大吗？</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
                  </summary>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2 text-sm">三家都提供OpenAI兼容格式的API。DeepSeek的API格式与OpenAI最为接近，迁移相对简单。Google AI使用不同格式，但提供迁移指南。</p>
                </details>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 结论 -->
          <section class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl border border-indigo-100 p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-900 mb-4">结论</h2>
            <p class="text-indigo-800 mb-4">
              对于<strong>国内开发者</strong>，DeepSeek是务实之选：直连访问、极低价格、足够的能力表现。接入无摩擦，成本可预测。
            </p>
            <p class="text-indigo-800 mb-4">
              对于<strong>国际产品</strong>或需要绝对最佳模型质量的任务，尽管需要代理，OpenAI仍是首选。
            </p>
            <p class="text-indigo-800 mb-4">
              对于<strong>长上下文或多模态应用</strong>，且预算有限，Google AI的Gemini 2.5 Flash值得考虑——但前提是你能稳定访问它。
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 mt-6">
              <a href="/zh/providers/deepseek" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-green-600 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">
                国内开发者首选 DeepSeek →
              </a>
              <a href="/zh/providers/openai" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors text-sm">
                追求最佳质量选 OpenAI →
              </a>
              <a href="/zh/providers/google" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-purple-600 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors text-sm">
                追求极致性价比选 Google AI →
              </a>
            </div>
          </section>

